_sText:
Since I've been unable to find the original Moo's b4 release of this fantastic map CBBLE, I decided to re-release it while adding a bit of eye candy.

--version 4.5--
Specific changes include:

- More optimization!! (Is that even possible?)
- Tweaked lightning in interior zones
- Added HDR for extra eye candy
- Cubemaps for your everyday reflection
- Environment changes such as new skymap, sun color, sun sprites...
- Adjusted some spots a few inches to make them more challenging (specially the MOO place)

Hope you enjoy! Feel free to point out whatever you want.
